This study will use an automated blood pressure monitor (Microlife WatchBP03) with an inbuilt algorithm to detect atrial fibrillation (an irregular heart rhythm) in patients with an implanted pacemaker who have previously documented paroxysmal (intermittent) atrial fibrillation.

 This study will compare the Microlife device detected atrial fibrillation episodes to the pacemaker detected atrial fibrillation episodes.

